text: Nico Georgiadis (born 22 January 1996) is a Swiss chess player. He holds the title of Grandmaster, which FIDE awarded him in 2017. ==Chess career== Born in Bülach, Georgiadis earned his international master title in 2013 and his grandmaster title in 2017.Der 21-jährige "Nico Georgiadis (Schindellegi) ist Grossmeister!".
